{"id":"lyr_5bCP6Zuq_MjMzMA_0025","text":"別和自己對抗 就算勝利仍受創","structure":{"line_index":25,"char_count":13},"semantics":{"themes":["停止內耗","接受現實"],"sentiment":"NEUTRAL","keywords":["對抗","受創"]},"prosody":{"tone_pattern":[2,0,2,9,4,4,2,4,4,2,0,2,3],"tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping":["bit6","wo4","zi6","gei2","deoi3","kong3","zau6","syun3","sing3","lei6","jing4","sau6","cong1"]},"nlp":{"tokens":[{"text":"別","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"和","pos":"ADP"},{"text":"自己","pos":"PRON"},{"text":"對抗","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"就算","pos":"CONJ"},{"text":"勝利","pos":"NOUN"},{"text":"仍受","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"創","pos":"NOUN"}],"syntax_notes":"勸告自己停止內耗，即使勝利也可能帶來傷害，語氣趨於理性。"},"source":{"title":"菩薩","artists":["小雪"],"lyricists":["黃偉文"],"year":0,"genre":["Pop","Cantopop"]},"context_links":{"doc_id":"feitsui_2330","prev_line_id":"lyr_5bCP6Zuq_MjMzMA_0024","next_line_id":"lyr_5bCP6Zuq_MjMzMA_0026","paragraph_id":"para_04"}}
{"id":"lyr_5bCP6Zuq_MjMzMA_0026","text":"忽然不想殺生","structure":{"line_index":26,"char_count":6},"semantics":{"themes":["轉變","放棄仇恨"],"sentiment":"NEUTRAL","keywords":["忽然","不想","殺生"]},"prosody":{"tone_pattern":[3,0,3,9,4,3],"tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping":["fat1","jin4","bat1","soeng2","saat3","sang1"]},"nlp":{"tokens":[{"text":"忽然","pos":"ADV"},{"text":"不想","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"殺生","pos":"VERB"}],"syntax_notes":"重複的段落，再次強調情感的轉折，從報復轉為放棄傷害。"},"source":{"title":"菩薩","artists":["小雪"],"lyricists":["黃偉文"],"year":0,"genre":["Pop","Cantopop"]},"context_links":{"doc_id":"feitsui_2330","prev_line_id":"lyr_5bCP6Zuq_MjMzMA_0025","next_line_id":"lyr_5bCP6Zuq_MjMzMA_0027","paragraph_id":"para_05"}}
{"id":"lyr_5bCP6Zuq_MjMzMA_0027","text":"用我的半生 當作祭品","structure":{"line_index":27,"char_count":9},"semantics":{"themes":["犧牲","奉獻"],"sentiment":"POSITIVE","keywords":["半生","祭品"]},"prosody":{"tone_pattern":[2,5,3,4,3,4,4,9],"tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping":["jung6","ngo5","dik1","bun3","sang1","zok3","zai3","ban2"]},"nlp":{"tokens":[{"text":"用","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"我","pos":"PRON"},{"text":"的","pos":"PART"},{"text":"半生","pos":"NOUN"},{"text":"當作","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"祭品","pos":"NOUN"}],"syntax_notes":"重複的段落，將自己的生命奉獻，語氣帶有犧牲的意味，但情感上趨向平靜。"},"source":{"title":"菩薩","artists":["小雪"],"lyricists":["黃偉文"],"year":0,"genre":["Pop","Cantopop"]},"context_links":{"doc_id":"feitsui_2330","prev_line_id":"lyr_5bCP6Zuq_MjMzMA_0026","next_line_id":"lyr_5bCP6Zuq_MjMzMA_0028","paragraph_id":"para_05"}}
{"id":"lyr_5bCP6Zuq_MjMzMA_0028","text":"不願踩得更深","structure":{"line_index":28,"char_count":6},"semantics":{"themes":["停止傷害","自我保護"],"sentiment":"NEUTRAL","keywords":["不願","踩得更深"]},"prosody":{"tone_pattern":[3,2,9,3,3],"tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping":["bat1","jyun6","caai2","dak1","sam1"]},"nlp":{"tokens":[{"text":"不願","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"踩得","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"更深","pos":"ADJ"}],"syntax_notes":"重複的段落，表達不願再加深傷害，有停止的意願。"},"source":{"title":"菩薩","artists":["小雪"],"lyricists":["黃偉文"],"year":0,"genre":["Pop","Cantopop"]},"context_links":{"doc_id":"feitsui_2330","prev_line_id":"lyr_5bCP6Zuq_MjMzMA_0027","next_line_id":"lyr_5bCP6Zuq_MjMzMA_0029","paragraph_id":"para_05"}}
